Audio.html
---------------------------
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Single Audio with Controls on Web Page</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Use of Audio on Web Page Using HTML5</h1>
    <audio src="file_example_MP3_5MG.mp3" controls autoplay loop>
        Your browser does not support the <code>audio</code> element.
    </audio>
</body>
</html>
================================================================================================
Audio1.html
------------------------------------------------
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Audio on Web Page</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Use of Audio on Web Page Using HTML5</h1>
    <audio controls autoplay>
        <source src="file_example_MP3_5MG.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
        <source src="file_example_OOG_5MG.ogg" type="audio/ogg">
        <source src="file_example_WAV_5MG.wav" type="audio/wav">
        Your browser does not support the <code>audio</code> element.
    </audio>
</body>
</html>
